{
  "texts": [
    "These deployments demonstrate that the infrastructure for sophisticated multi-agent research systems already exists.The described protocols also create powerful possibilities for economic research workflows.",
    "Consider a research project investigating the employment effects of AI adoption.",
    "A lead research agent may connect to multiple data sources through MCP servers -BLS employment statistics, company financial reports, patent databases, or academic paper repositories.",
    "Each connection uses the same standardized protocol, eliminating integration complexity.",
    "The lead agent can then delegate subtasks to specialized agents, e.g., data cleaning agents, financial analysis agents, econometric agents, visualization agents, etc."
  ]
}